
= founder of Red Hat


=Bio=

"Bob Young created Red Hat, one of the most successful free software companies. Under young’s leadership, Red Hat established itself as the leading GNU/Linux distribution in the server space. Red Hat’s contributions to the Linux kernel and free software in general are immense."
